# UI conventions

- Reuse existing feature components and `components/ui/*` (shadcn / Base UI). Prefer extending over new primitives.
- Pages are Server Components by default; add `'use client'` only for interactivity (forms, nav, charts, calendars).
- Forms that mutate data call Server Actions (often via `useActionState` / form `action`) — match nearby forms.
- Layout: `NavBar` + main content; hide nav on `/login`, `/signup`, `/onboarding` (see `HIDDEN_ROUTES`).
- Profile page hosts both `ProfileEditForm` and `ReminderSettings` — keep reminder opt-in there unless asked to move it.
- Styling: Tailwind v4 + CSS variables in `app/globals.css`. Fonts: body = Plus Jakarta Sans, display/heading = Orbitron (`font-heading`).
- Dark theme is the product default (`className="dark"` on `<html>`). Preserve the existing look; don't restyle the app unless asked.
- Shared types live in `lib/types.ts`. Don't duplicate Profile/Checkin shapes in components.
